<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Billi Mucklow and her footballer fiancé Andy Carroll have revealed they've named their newborn daughter Marvel Mae.</p>

<p>Former TOWIE star Billi, 32, and Newcastle United striker Andy, 31, took to their respective Instagram accounts on Tuesday to share an adorable snap of their precious bundle of joy, as they also unveiled her name.</p>

<p>Captioning the image, which showed little Marvel perched on her mother's chest as she wore cosy knitwear – and sported a lipstick kiss on her cheek – Billi wrote: 'Marvel Mae Carroll... And Marvellous You Are My Little Lady.'</p>

<p>Marvellous! Billi Mucklow and her footballer fiancé Andy Carroll revealed they've named their newborn daughter Marvel Mae as they shared a snap of the newborn on Tuesday</p>

<p>Sportsman Andy shared his own caption on his account, writing: 'Marvel Mae Carroll ❤️ Fairy Tales Do Come True. Look At Us We Had You.'</p>

<p>On Friday, the couple proved they are very much living in a blissful bubble with their new addition as they shared a video showing their arrival home with the newborn. </p>

<p>In a clip showing his daughter Emilie Rose, who celebrated her 11th birthday on the same day of her sister's birth, waiting at the door, the parents looked overjoyed before Billi shared a series of sweet snaps.</p>

<p>News: Billi Mucklow and Andy Carroll shared the news on their respective Instagram accounts</p>

<p>Captions: The doting parents each added their own captions as they shared the same snapshot</p>

<p>Billi looked to be taking things slowly as she headed into the house in a black dress while the Newcastle United ace, held her suitcase and the car seat.</p>

<p>She then shared a video of their adorable baby in the tot and also images of their entire brood gently greeting the new addition to the family. </p>

<p>Continuing their social media activity, Andy shared a family portrait on Thursday.</p>

<p>He was every inch the doting dad as he took to Instagram to share a snap with his 208,000 followers showing Emilie cradling the newborn alongside his other kids. </p>

<p>He is father to Emilie Rose and Lucas, nine, from a previous relationship, while he shares Arlo, four, and Wolf, two, with his partner of seven years, Billie.  </p>

